instruction:
给定电磁场张量 $F_{\mu
u}$ 和四维电流密度 $j_{
u}$，验证麦克斯韦方程组的协变形式 $ rac{\partial F_{\mu
u}}{\partial x_{\mu}} = \mu_0 j_{
u}$ 在 $
u = 0$ 时的具体形式。

output:
 - 题目要求先写出叉乘结果再进行旋度运算，所以需要分别完成这两个步骤。</think>
首先明确题目要求，需按顺序先算出$\pmb{A}\times\pmb{B}$，然后再对其求旋度$\nabla\times(\pmb{A}\times\pmb{B})$ 。对于叉乘部分，根据向量叉乘定义及单位向量运算规则来展开计算；对旋度部分，利用已知的叉乘结果代入旋度相关公式进行推导。</think>
<answer>
1. **计算$\pmb{A}\times\pmb{B}$**：
   已知$\pmb{A}=x^{2}\hat{x}+y^{2}\hat{y}+z^{2}\hat{z}$，$\pmb{B}=y\hat{x}+z\hat{y}+x\hat{z}$，由向量叉乘公式$(\vec{\alpha}\times\vec{\beta})_{i}=\epsilon_{ijk}\alpha_{j}\beta_{k}$（其中$i,j,k$为指标），可得：
   \[
   \begin{align*}
   &\left(x^{2}\hat{x}+y^{2}\hat{y}+z^{2}\hat{z}\right)\times(y\hat{x}+z\hat{y}+x\hat{z})
   \\&=(x^{2}(z)-(y^{2})(x))\hat{x}+(y^{2}(x)-(z^{2})(y))\hat{y}+(z^{2}(y)-(x^{2})(z))\hat{z}
   \\&=(xz^{2}-xy^{2})\hat{x}+(yx^{2}-yz^{2})\hat{y}+(zy^{2}-zx^{2})\hat{z}
   \end{align*}
   \]
2. **计算$\nabla\times(\pmb{A}\times\pmb{B})$**：
   根据旋度公式$\nabla\times\vec{C}=\frac{\partial C_z}{\partial y}-\frac{\partial C_y}{\partial z}\hat{x}+\frac{\partial C_x}{\partial z}-\frac{\partial C_z}{\partial x}\hat{y}+\frac{\partial C_y}{\partial x}-\frac{\partial C_x}{\partial y}\hat{z}$，这里$\vec{C}=(xz^{2}-xy^{2})\hat{x}+(yx^{2}-yz^{2})\hat{y}+(zy^{2}-zx^{2})\hat{z}$，即$C_x=xz^{2}-xy^{2}$，$C_y=yx^{2}-yz^{2}$，$C_z=zy^{2}-zx^{2}$。
   则有：
   \[
   \begin{align*}
   &\frac{\partial (zy^{2}-zx^{2})}{\partial y}-\frac{\partial (yx^{2}-yz^{2})}{\partial z}\hat{x}+\frac{\partial (xz^{2}-xy^{2})}{\partial z}-\frac{\partial (zy^{2}-zx^{2})}{\partial x}\hat{y}+\frac{\partial (yx^{2}-yz^{2})}{\partial x}-\frac{\partial (xz^{2}-xy^{2})}{\partial y}\hat{z}
   \\&=[2zy - 0]\hat{x}+[2xz - (-2yz)]\hat{y}+[0 - 2zx](-\hat{z})
   \\&=(2zy)\hat{x}-(2xz-2yz)\hat{y}+(2zx)\hat{z}
   \\&=(2zy)\hat{x}+(2yz - 2xz)\hat{y}+(2zx)\hat{z}
   \end{align*}
   \]
</answer>

